dcterms:description: NIH ChestX-ray8 dataset consists of 112,120 chest X-ray images collected from 30,805 patients. It contains 8 diseases, including Atelectasis, Cardiomegaly, Effusion, Infiltration, Mass, Nodule, Pneumonia, and Pneumothorax. The labels are extracted from the associated radiology report by using an automatic labeler.
